  Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only: default-src * data: blob: filesystem: ws: wss: 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval'; script-src * 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' data: blob:; script-src-elem * 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' data: blob:; style-src * 'unsafe-inline'; img-src * data: blob:; font-src * data: blob:; connect-src * data: blob: ws: wss:; frame-src *; frame-ancestors *; object-src *; base-uri *; form-action *
